            </p>
          </div>

          <div className="mt-6">
            <span className="w-full text-center bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white font-extrabold text-[11px] py-2.5 rounded-full shadow-sm tracking-wider uppercase transition-colors block">
